      * description 0..1 CodeableConcept "Description" """[at0135] Narrative description about the service requested."""
      * clinicalIndication 0..* CodeableConcept "Clinical indication" """[at0152] The symptom, sign or diagnosis that necessitates the requested service."""
      * clinicalContext 0..1 CodeableConcept "Clinical context" """[at0154] Narrative information about the individual and their situation, providing relevant context for the request."""
      * reasonForRequest 0..* CodeableConcept "Reason for request" """[at0062] The specific problem needing attention or the clinical question that requires investigation."""
      * reasonDescription 0..1 CodeableConcept "Reason description" """[at0064] Narrative description about the issue or clinical query that needs resolution."""
      * intent 0..* CodeableConcept "Intent" """[at0065] Description of the intended outcome of the request."""
      * orderDetail 0..* CodeableConcept "Order detail" """[at0153] Additional details and instructions about how the services are to be delivered."""
      * urgency 0..1 CodeableConcept "Urgency" """[at0068] Urgency of the request for service."""
      * urgency from InternationalPatientSummaryUrgency (preferred)
      * serviceDue[x] 0..1 dateTime or CodeableConcept or BackboneElement "Service due" "at0040: The date/time or description about timing for provision of the requested service/s."
      * supplementaryInformation 0..1 boolean "Supplementary information" """[at0076] Supplementary information will be following request."""
      * informationDescription 0..1 CodeableConcept "Information description" """[at0078] Description of the supplementary information."""
      * comment 0..1 CodeableConcept "Comment" """[at0150] Additional narrative about the service request not captured in other fields."""
      * timing 1..1 string "Timing" """[RM] """
      * actionArchetypeId 1..1 string "Action_archetype_id" """[RM] """
    * requesterOrderIdentifier[x] 0..1 CodeableConcept or Identifier "Requester order identifier" "at0010: The local identifier assigned by the requesting clinical system."
    * receiverOrderIdentifier[x] 0..1 CodeableConcept or Identifier "Receiver order identifier" "at0011: The local identifier assigned to the request by the clinician or organisation receiving the request for service."
    * requestStatus 0..1 CodeableConcept "Request status" """[at0127] The status of the request for service as indicated by the requester."""
    * eligibilityGuidance 0..1 CodeableConcept "Eligibility guidance" """[at0158] Advice from the requester to the receiver about the individual's eligibility for the requested service."""
    * billingGuidance 0..1 CodeableConcept "Billing guidance" """[at0156] A recommendation from the requester to the receiver about the method of payment for the service."""
    * expiryTime 0..1 dateTime "expiry_time" """[RM] """
* functionalStatus 0..1 BackboneElement "Functional Status" """[openEHR-EHR-SECTION.adhoc.v1] A generic section header which should be renamed in a template to suit a specific clinical context."""
  * ProblemDiagnosis 0..1 BackboneElement "Problem/Diagnosis" """[openEHR-EHR-EVALUATION.problem_diagnosis.v1] Details about a single identified health condition, injury, disability or any other issue which impacts on the physical, mental and/or social well-being of an individual."""
    * problemDiagnosisName 1..1 CodeableConcept "Problem/Diagnosis name" """[at0002] Identification of the problem or diagnosis, by name."""
    * variant 0..* CodeableConcept "Variant" """[at0079] Specific variant or subtype of the Diagnosis, if relevant."""
    * bodySite 0..* CodeableConcept "Body site" """[at0012] Identification of a simple body site for the location of the problem or diagnosis."""
    * cause 0..* CodeableConcept "Cause" """[at0078] A cause, set of causes, or manner of causation of the problem or diagnosis."""
    * dateTimeOfOnset 0..1 dateTime "Date/time of onset" """[at0077] Estimated or actual date/time that signs or symptoms of the problem/diagnosis were first observed."""
    * severity 0..1 CodeableConcept "Severity" """[at0005] An assessment of the overall severity of the problem or diagnosis."""
    * severity from InternationalPatientSummarySeverity4 (preferred)
    * dateOfAbatement 0..1 dateTime "Date of abatement" """[at0030] Estimated or actual date/time of resolution or remission for this problem or diagnosis, as determined by a healthcare professional."""
    * problemDiagnosisQualifier 0..1 BackboneElement "Problem/Diagnosis qualifier" """[openEHR-EHR-CLUSTER.problem_qualifier.v2] Contextual or temporal qualifier for a specified problem or diagnosis."""
      * activeInactive 0..1 CodeableConcept "Active/Inactive?" """[at0003] Category that supports division of problems and diagnoses into Active or Inactive problem lists."""
      * activeInactive from InternationalPatientSummaryActiveInactive3 (required)
      * resolutionPhase 0..1 CodeableConcept "Resolution phase" """[at0083] Phase of healing for an acute problem or diagnosis."""
      * resolutionPhase from InternationalPatientSummaryResolutionPhase3 (required)
      * remissionStatus 0..1 CodeableConcept "Remission status" """[at0089] Status of the remission of an incurable diagnosis."""
      * remissionStatus from InternationalPatientSummaryRemissionStatus3 (required)
      * occurrence 0..1 CodeableConcept "Occurrence" """[at0071] Category of the occurrence for this problem or diagnosis."""
      * occurrence from InternationalPatientSummaryOccurrence3 (required)
    * diagnosticCertainty 0..1 CodeableConcept "Diagnostic certainty" """[at0073] The level of confidence in the identification of the diagnosis."""
    * diagnosticCertainty from InternationalPatientSummaryDiagnosticCertainty3 (preferred)
    * lastUpdated 0..1 dateTime "Last updated" """[at0070] The date this problem or diagnosis was last updated."""
  * ClinicalImpression 0..1 BackboneElement "Clinical impression" """[openEHR-EHR-EVALUATION.clinical_synopsis.v1] Narrative summary or overview about a patient, specifically from the perspective of a healthcare provider, and with or without associated interpretations."""
    * impression 1..1 CodeableConcept "Impression" """[at0002] The summary, assessment, conclusions or evaluation of the clinical findings."""

